юTO COMMEMORATE THE 150TH ANNIVERSARY OF
THE CHURCH OF JESUS CHRIST OF LATTER-DAY SAINTS IN THE BRITISH ISLES 26 JULY 1987
ON THE MORNING OF 19 MAY 1840, ORSON PRATT, AN EARLY APOSTLE OF THE CHURCH,
CLIMBED TO THE TOP OF ARTHUR'S SEAT IN HOLYROOD PARK AND IN MIGHTY PRAYER
DEDICATED THE COUNTRY OF SCOTLAND FOR THE PREACHING OF THE RESTORED GOSPEL OF JESUS CHRIST"ґ
